name: Venusaur-EX

name: Weedle

Attack1Text: Your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Poisoned.

Attack2Text: This attack does 10 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

Attack1Text: Choose 1 of your opponent's Active Pokémon's attacks. That Pokémon can't use that attack during your opponent's next turn.

Attack1Text: Flip 4 coins. This attack does 10 damage times the number of heads.

Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, prevent all damage done to this Pokémon by attacks during your opponent's next turn.

Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.

Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, search your deck for a Supporter card, reveal it, and put it into your hand. Shuffle your deck afterward.

Attack2Text: You may do 20 more damage. If you do, this Pokémon does 20 damage to itself.

name: Slugma

Attack1Text: Discard an Energy attached to this Pokémon.

name: Magcargo

Attack1Text: You may discard the top card of your deck. If that card is a Fire Energy card, this attack does 50 more damage.

name: Blastoise-EX

Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.

Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.

Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, discard an Energy attached to 1 of your opponent's Pokémon.

name: Blastoise-EX
Attack1Text: Switch this Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon. Then, your opponent switches his or her Active Pokémon with 1 of his or her Benched Pokémon.
Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If tails, this Pokémon does 30 damage to itself.

name: Emolga-EX
Attack1Text: Search your deck for a Lightning Energy card and attach it to this Pokémon. Shuffle your deck afterward. If you attached Energy in this way, switch this Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon.
Attack2Text: You may discard an Energy attached to this Pokémon. If you do, this attack does 30 more damage.

name: Yveltal-EX
Attack1Text: This attack does 20 more damage times the amount of Energy attached to both Active Pokémon.
Attack2Text: Move an Energy from this Pokémon to 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

name: Skarmory-EX
Attack1Text: Before doing damage, discard all Pokémon Tool cards attached to your opponent's Active Pokémon.
Attack2Text: If your opponent's Active Pokémon already has any damage counters on it, this attack does 40 more damage.

name: Xerneas-EX
Attack1Text: This attack does 30 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)
Attack2Text: This Pokémon can't use X Blast during your next turn.
